          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39139657/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39139657/" class="">第84页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/73879939/" class=" " title="李大日宣">李大日宣</a>
                (你所经历的，世人夺不去。)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="39139657">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">84 如果做了善事还要备受一些什么都没做的人指责，好人会越来越少，做事的人会越来越谨慎。
